Important Announcement: Opening of Portal for Registration for 2nd Semester, 2016/2017 Academic Session

This is to inform students of the University of Lagos that the portal for registration for the 2nd Semester, 2016/2017 Academic Session opened on Monday, May 1, 2017 and will be closed on Sunday, June 18, 2017.

Students who have requested for permission to pay their obligatory charges in 2nd Semester, 2016/2017 Session should pay through the REMITTA platform at any bank.

All students are advised to take advantage of this opportunity to register for the semester accordingly.
